    {
      "repository": "gordolio/Trio",
      "number": 1200,
      "title": "Remove Legacy Omnipod Submodules (OmniKit, OmniBLE)",
      "body": "## Summary\r\nRemoves the legacy `OmniBLE` (DASH) and `OmniKit` (Eros) submodules and all their platform-specific code paths, consolidating both Omnipod variants under the new `OmnipodKit` submodule (`OmniPumpManager`), added and shipped with Trio `v0.8.1`.\r\n\r\n**Changes:**\r\n- Deletes `OmniBLE` and `OmniKit` git submodules and their `.gitmodules` entries\r\n- Bumps `OmnipodKit` to `d68699c`\r\n- Removes `OmniBLEPumpManager` and `OmnipodPumpManager` from `staticPumpManagers`, `DeviceDataManager`, `PumpSetupView`, and all pump-type enums — replaced by `OmniPumpManager`\r\n- Collapses the separate \"Omnipod Eros\" / \"Omnipod DASH\" pump-selection buttons into a single \"All Omnipod Types\" entry in `HomeRootView` and `PumpConfigRootView`\r\n- Merges `omnipodEros` / `omnipodDash` onboarding enum cases into a single `.omni` case; adds a `FIXME` noting that Eros min-basal-rate differentiation is not yet handled\r\n- Removes OmniBLE/OmniKit build targets, framework references, and test schemes from `project.pbxproj` and `Trio.xcscheme`\r\n- Drops OmniBLE/OmniKit Crowdin localisation sources and swiftformat exclusions\r\n- Updates telemetry comment and `PRIVACY_POLICY.md` to reference OmnipodKit instead of OmniBLE\r\n\r\n**Note:** The `.omni` onboarding basal-rate picker currently uses the DASH minimum (0 U/hr). Eros requires a minimum of 0.05 U/hr but the two variants can no longer be distinguished at that step — tracked in the inline `FIXME`.",
      "labels": [],
      "url": "https://github.com/nightscout/Trio/pull/1200",
      "mergedAt": "2026-06-13T01:55:44Z"
    },
    {
      "repository": "nightscout/Trio",
      "number": 1200,
      "title": "Remove Legacy Omnipod Submodules (OmniKit, OmniBLE)",
      "body": "## Summary\r\nRemoves the legacy `OmniBLE` (DASH) and `OmniKit` (Eros) submodules and all their platform-specific code paths, consolidating both Omnipod variants under the new `OmnipodKit` submodule (`OmniPumpManager`), added and shipped with Trio `v0.8.1`.\r\n\r\n**Changes:**\r\n- Deletes `OmniBLE` and `OmniKit` git submodules and their `.gitmodules` entries\r\n- Bumps `OmnipodKit` to `d68699c`\r\n- Removes `OmniBLEPumpManager` and `OmnipodPumpManager` from `staticPumpManagers`, `DeviceDataManager`, `PumpSetupView`, and all pump-type enums — replaced by `OmniPumpManager`\r\n- Collapses the separate \"Omnipod Eros\" / \"Omnipod DASH\" pump-selection buttons into a single \"All Omnipod Types\" entry in `HomeRootView` and `PumpConfigRootView`\r\n- Merges `omnipodEros` / `omnipodDash` onboarding enum cases into a single `.omni` case; adds a `FIXME` noting that Eros min-basal-rate differentiation is not yet handled\r\n- Removes OmniBLE/OmniKit build targets, framework references, and test schemes from `project.pbxproj` and `Trio.xcscheme`\r\n- Drops OmniBLE/OmniKit Crowdin localisation sources and swiftformat exclusions\r\n- Updates telemetry comment and `PRIVACY_POLICY.md` to reference OmnipodKit instead of OmniBLE\r\n\r\n**Note:** The `.omni` onboarding basal-rate picker currently uses the DASH minimum (0 U/hr). Eros requires a minimum of 0.05 U/hr but the two variants can no longer be distinguished at that step — tracked in the inline `FIXME`.",
      "labels": [],
      "url": "https://github.com/nightscout/Trio/pull/1200",
      "mergedAt": "2026-06-13T01:55:44Z"
    },
    {
      "repository": "gordolio/Trio",
      "number": 1212,
      "title": "Trio v0.8.2 patch release ",
      "body": "## What's Changed At A Glance\r\n\r\n- **OmnipodKit is now the sole Omnipod driver** — OmniBLE and OmniKit submodules removed; \"All Omnipod Types\" is the only Omnipod entry in Add Pump and Onboarding\r\n- **Live Activity Enhancements / Fixes:**\r\n   -  Temp target on chart — active temp targets now render as a green band on the Live Activity chart, with a named badge alongside the override badge\r\n   - Ondefinite override fix — overrides with no set duration no longer collapse the chart's rule mark to the current moment\r\n   - COB label and widget string fixes — corrected the COB string and localized all widget item labels\r\n- **Watch connectivity fix** — massively improve watch performance; stale data on watch now updates in just a moment vs. getting stuck during processing.\r\n- **Fix Stats Meals showing zero macros for current day** — today's carbs, fat, and protein now always appear correctly in the Meals chart\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Full List of PRs in `0.8.2`\r\n\r\n| PR | Title | Author |\r\n|---|---|---|\r\n| [#1180](https://github.com/nightscout/Trio/pull/1180) | Add temp target display to Live Activity lock screen widget | [@t1dude](https://github.com/t1dude) |\r\n| [#1182](https://github.com/nightscout/Trio/pull/1182) | Update CODEOWNERS: add @marionbarker and @kingst | [@dnzxy](https://github.com/dnzxy) |\r\n| [#1184](https://github.com/nightscout/Trio/pull/1184) | Fix COB string, localize Live Activity widget item labels | [@dnzxy](https://github.com/dnzxy) |\r\n| [#1188](https://github.com/nightscout/Trio/pull/1188) | Fix Stats Meals showing zero macros for current day | [@dnzxy](https://github.com/dnzxy) |\r\n| [#1190](https://github.com/nightscout/Trio/pull/1190) | Fix watch app back-sync after long staleness | [@dnzxy](https://github.com/dnzxy) |\r\n| [#1192](https://github.com/nightscout/Trio/pull/1192) | Fix indefinite override not drawn in Live Activity chart | [@t1dude](https://github.com/t1dude) |\r\n| [#1200](https://github.com/nightscout/Trio/pull/1200) | Remove Legacy Omnipod Submodules (OmniKit, OmniBLE) | [@dnzxy](https://github.com/dnzxy) |\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Contributors\r\n\r\n@dnzxy @t1dude @marv-out ",
      "labels": [],
      "url": "https://github.com/nightscout/Trio/pull/1212",
      "mergedAt": "2026-06-15T20:43:56Z"
    },
